 <title xml:id="General">Disable Software RAID Monitor</title>
 <para>
  Disable the Software RAID Monitor (<filename>mdmonitor</filename>)
  service. This service is extraneous unless software RAID is in use.
  <indexterm>
   <primary>mdmonitor</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <indexterm>
   <primary>RAID</primary>
  </indexterm>
 </para>
